      • getStatement

        public Statement getStatement()
        Gets the statement value for this ReportQuery.
        Returns:
        statement * Specifies a filter to use for reporting on data. This filter will be used in conjunction (joined with an AND statement) with the date range selected through dateRangeType, startDate, and endDate and the dimension filters selected through dimensionFilters. The syntax currently allowed for Statement.query is [WHERE {AND ...}]


             := =

             := =
        := IN
        := :
         where property is the enumeration name of a Dimension that can be filtered.

        For example, the statement "WHERE LINE_ITEM_ID IN (34344, 23235)" can be used to generate a report for a specific set of line items

        Filtering on IDs is highly recommended over filtering on names, especially for geographical entities. When filtering on names, matching is case sensitive.
